"```sql\nSELECT AVG(s.NumTstTakr) AS average_test_takers\nFROM satscores s\nJOIN schools sch ON s.cds = sch.CDSCode\nWHERE sch.County = 'Fresno'\n  AND YEAR(sch.OpenDate) = 1980;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the average number of SAT test takers from schools in Fresno County that opened in the year 1980. It joins the `satscores` table with the `schools` table using the foreign key relationship between `satscores.cds` and `schools.CDSCode`. The query filters the results to include only those schools located in Fresno County and with an opening date in the year 1980."